items.subtitle: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on 3 November 2023
items.title: This iPhone SE is good but can be better.
items.review_text: I liked how it was small and fit in my hand. I also liked how it retained a headphone jack. I did not like the storage space being extremely limited. It was only 32GB. I also did not like how it was not water resistant. There is another version of this same type of phone with 128GB storage which is more efficient. I found that on OnBuy. I used this phone for daily activities like messaging, calling, watching videos, cooking and doing sports.

items.subtitle: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on 14 October 2023
items.title: Great quality but expensive
items.review_text: The phone looks exactly as it it has just come out of the factory, perfect in every way. With hindsight though almost £100 for a six year old phone seems a bit much, in particular as it will not be able to use the newer IOS.

items.subtitle: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on 19 April 2023
items.title: Phone mic was poor
items.review_text:
It arrived within two days but had problems people say the voice chat is very poor and cannot hear clearly
Asked for replacement had quick reply then nothing from seller still trying to get a reply they offered a replacement and details would be sent to return this item but then silent from them
Tried to phone no reply sent e mail and sent message via Amazon so far no reply
Hopefully they will reply other than that phones in good condition
